issues.body:
many videos uploaded are 1080p and even 4k , which is quite a lot for low internet speed users 
you can add support for multi-quality by converting every video uploaded automatically via php and ffmpeg (or vlc if you like) , and when viewing the vid user has choice to choose between qualities ex. 240 , 360 , 480 , etc 

here is example of php code , please implement it to your site 

<?php 
if (isset($_POST['submit'])) {
	$currentPath=$_FILES['video']['tmp_name'];
	exec("ffmpeg.exe"); 
	exec("ffmpeg -i ".$currentPath." -an ./output/video.mp4");

	echo "Ok";

}



 ?>

full list of files
https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/0B1i-7bcQfbKPd1hGRHRfRThCUVE

n.b: you can have the same results with vlc
